{"lemma":"طِيرَةٌ","slug":"طِيرَةٌ","root":"ط.#.ر","root_slug":"ط-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27449","n27455","n27456"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"giddiness, levity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"slip, stumble"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a kind of swift boat"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"augury, ornithomancy"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pessimism","tags":["broadly"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ط ي ر (ṭ y r) and طَيْر (ṭayr) + ـَة (-a)."},"ipa":["/tˤaj.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27449","headword_ar":"طيّرهُ","root":"Tyr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~r bihi","text_ar":"طيّر بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ATArhu","text_ar":"اطارهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAyrhu","text_ar":"طايرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAra","text_ar":"طَارَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to fly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, K.) [See also 10.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ara AlEaSaAfiyra","text_ar":"طَيَّرَ العَصَافِيرَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani Alz~aroEi","text_ar":"عَنِ الزَّرْعِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the sparrows to fly away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scared them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersed them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the seedproduce."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo fiY $aYo'K laA yuTay~aru guraAbuhu","text_ar":"هُمْ فِى شَىْءٍ لَا يُطَيَّرُ غُرَابُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are in that whereof the crow is not made to fly away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of its abundance]: a prov. alluding to a state of plenty. (S, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guraAbN","text_ar":"غُرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uTiyra AlguraAbu","text_ar":"اُطِيرَ الغُرَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The crow was made to fly away"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTaArN","text_ar":"مُطَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~r","text_ar":"طيّر"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuw^aAdahu","text_ar":"فُوَادَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made his courage"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his heart"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to fly away"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fz","text_ar":"فز"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~r","text_ar":"طيّر"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaAla bayona Alqawomi","text_ar":"المَالَ بَيْنَ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ATArhu","text_ar":"اطارهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He divided the property into lots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shares, among the people:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, * TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTarotu","text_ar":"اَطَرْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I divided into lots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shares,"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad.; but some say that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a radical letter. (IAth, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~r AlfaHolu AlA_ibila","text_ar":"طيّر الفَحْلُ الاـِبِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stallion made all the she-camels to conceive:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to conceive quickly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~arato hiYa","text_ar":"طَيَّرَتْ هِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tuy~irato","text_ar":"طُيِّرَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"?]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They conceived quickly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27455","headword_ar":"طَيْرَةٌ","root":"Tyr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayoruwrapN","text_ar":"طَيْرُورَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayorN","text_ar":"طَيْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Levity; inconstancy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY fulaAnK","text_ar":"فِى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayorapN","text_ar":"طَيْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayoruwrapN","text_ar":"طَيْرُورَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In such a one is levity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inconstancy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Auzojuro A^aHonaA='a Tayorika","text_ar":"اُزْجُرْ اَحْنَا=ءَ طَيْرِكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [alluding to the original signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayorN","text_ar":"طَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", namely, “ birds, ”] means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAniba xif~atika waTayo$ika","text_ar":"جَوَانِبَ خِفَّتِكَ وَطَيْشِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[agreeing with an explanation of the same saying voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HinowN","text_ar":"حِنْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (S.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayorapN","text_ar":"طَيْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A slip; a stumble:"},{"kind":"text","text":"hence the trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iy~aAka waTayoraAti Al$~abaAbi","text_ar":"اـِيَّاكَ وَطَيْرَاتِ الشَّبَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beware thou of the slips and stumbles of youth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27456","headword_ar":"طِيْرَةٌ","root":"Tyr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiyarapN","text_ar":"طِيَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiwarapN","text_ar":"طِوَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^irN","text_ar":"طَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the second, in four places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}